               </ab>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Wednesday 6th Feby. 1805</hi>.    clear and pleasant    the Savages trouble us verry much. <name type="person" key="Lewis, Meriwether">Capt Lewis</name> took his observations. <name type="person" key="Shields, John">Shields</name> went out towards evening to hunt &amp; killed 3 Goats which we brought in and eat the meat.—


</p>
